{"tid":1439403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"OL兼Model孫凱怡斥示威者搞事自私","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T08:26:01.000Z","uid":85099,"like":5,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"15e419f81d2293ef1f3616e7006832cf962a88cb","tid":1439403,"uid":85099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"香港特區政府擬修訂逃犯條例而惹起大批市民的不滿，引發了連串的反修例行動，包括大型的遊行、示威和抗議等，並向政府提出了五大訴求，不過特首林鄭月娥至今仍未回應，令到爭取政府回應訴求的市民、多個團體以及工會於昨日（5日）參與罷工行動，藉此來向政府施壓。而昨日的罷工以及連串不合作行動引起了交通大混亂，路面道路多處出現堵塞情況，港鐵多條線的服務更一度癱瘓，導致要上班的市民受到影響。一位自稱在中環任職OL的Model孫凱怡 (Penny) 對此大表不滿。<br />\n<br />\nPenny除了在中環做OL，其實她還有從事Freelance model的工作，之前也有出席過品牌的公開活動，報道曾以藝人來稱呼她。昨日Penny於荔景站接受《香港01》直播的訪問時，就斥責進行不合作運動阻塞港鐵的示威者阻住她以及一班市民返工，表示：「我覺得好過分，完全唔諗人感受，係好自私嘅行為。政府係有做得唔好嘅地方，但係我覺得 (示威者) 唔需要做到咁囉。依家咁阻住，可能要去探病或者睇醫生 (嘅人) 咁點呢？有無諗過其他人接唔接受你 (示威者) 咁做？其實只係少部分人咁做咋喎。」<br />\n<br />\nPenny自言並不清楚昨日會有示威者堵塞地鐵，又多次強調示威者的不合作運動好自私，她說：「我唔知可以點做，佢哋有無幫我哋諗下可以點做？」她又力撐香港政府表示：「政府依家做咗啲咩咁嚴重呢？我覺得依家經濟繁榮，嚟緊會有好大嘅問題咁邊個去負責？個個都失業咁點呢？你返屋企堵塞唔好畀你父母返工先啦，你點解要阻住其他市民？呢個行為好過分囉。」其實Penny之前亦有於她的facebook出post指責示威者破壞公物。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/360493/8-5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-ol%E5%85%BCmodel%E5%AD%AB%E5%87%B1%E6%80%A1%E6%96%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%90%9E%E4%BA%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BE%9D%E5%AE%B6%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%B9%81%E6%A6%AE?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Tt--BUSzaV57Co0NrxTKnOwP1-X-1fLApwA5T_5Kztpuobd_KpsToCms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F360493%2F8-5%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5-ol%25E5%2585%25BCmodel%25E5%25AD%25AB%25E5%2587%25B1%25E6%2580%25A1%25E6%2596%25A5%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%2590%259E%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A7%2581-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BE%259D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E7%25B9%2581%25E6%25A6%25AE%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dentertainment%26fbclid%3DIwAR2Tt--BUSzaV57Co0NrxTKnOwP1-X-1fLApwA5T_5Kztpuobd_KpsToCms&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s4eonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=2392ce69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/360493/8-5%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-ol%E5%85%BCmodel%E5%AD%AB%E5%87%B1%E6%80%A1%E6%96%A5%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%90%9E%E4%BA%8B%E8%87%AA%E7%A7%81-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BE%9D%E5%AE%B6%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%B9%81%E6%A6%AE?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=entertainment&amp;fbclid=IwAR2Tt--BUSzaV57Co0NrxTKnOwP1-X-1fLApwA5T_5Kztpuobd_KpsToCms</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死臭雞"},{"pid":"666a21c45d85c6174bc3df193a41ec13b432c7d8","tid":1439403,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:49:31.000Z","msg":"dont make stupid people famous"},{"pid":"9fbefab4c43feb30484c7581a4ab66eb330f0c8b","tid":1439403,"uid":18959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:50:13.000Z","msg":"請善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"f1cf8fb2e90eff0be75e4c7b54886c9f86d89248","tid":1439403,"uid":128794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"不推"},{"pid":"a6a491664b8fa6f44ed91c9dd62b8d0a1462eacf","tid":1439403,"uid":59570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:52:11.000Z","msg":"唔好推，唔好幫d雞宣傳"},{"pid":"c8e8e827375459f3553f6fdb2f489daa3e426cf4","tid":1439403,"uid":133977,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:52:20.000Z","msg":"Ol+model=g"},{"pid":"56d48c23987254b4c12dcedd7a749dfacc69d891","tid":1439403,"uid":262914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"d5b0a074e2584cfda6810351329ce5305a8f8bd4","tid":1439403,"uid":176657,"li